    观察者模式

    前言:观察者模式又称发布-订阅模式,主要用来解耦对象之间的依赖.简单点说,当发布对象 发生属性改变时,通知其他对象.

    # 01、观察者模式

    # -*- ecoding: utf-8 -*-
# @ModuleName: observer
# @Mail: 15717163552@163.com
# @Author: mozhouqiu
# @Time: 2022/4/29 14:29
class Publish:
    def __init__(self):
        self.registerList=[]

    def register(self,register):
        self.registerList.append(register)


    def notify(self,num):
        for register in self.registerList:
            register.update(num)


class Register:
    def __init__(self):
        self.num = 0

    def update(self,num):
        self.num = num

p1 = Publish()
r1 = Register()
r2 = Register()
p1.register(r1)
p1.register(r2)
p1.notify(2)
print(r1.num)
print(r2.num)
